    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Stops spam on comments box. User needs to enter result of a simple math problem in a text box before posting a comment. User will only be prompted if not logged in. It&#8217;s a simple to use plugin that won&#8217;t leave your user frustrated when trying to post. <a href=\"http://stopjunk.megatag.me\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Try the demo here.</a></p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload <code>stop-junk</code> directory to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Set the color of the verfication text by clicking the <code>Stop Junk Plugin</code> menu under the Plugins folder in WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First version.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
